#: src/gui/gui.cc:2207
msgid "Fast boot"
msgstr "Γρήγορη εκκίνηση"

#: src/gui/gui.cc:2208
msgid ""
"This will cause the BIOS to skip the shell,\n"
"which may include additional checks.\n"
"Also will make the boot time substantially\n"
"faster by not displaying the logo."
